      "role": "user",
      "content": "that outline looks good. let's dive into the \"business attire\" part first. i want to make sure my readers know what the actual standard is for being professional. like, if they are at a high-end gala or a big business meeting, what's the go-to look that everyone recognizes as sophisticated? can u give me some specific examples of what \"standard\" professional clothing looks like?",
